TOYOTA U TRUST

Toyota Kirloskar Motors in India started the Toyota U Trust Program in 2007. Our main aim is to provide the used car buyer and sellers an experience at par with a New Car buyer.

Each car is purchased at a fair price and goes through extensive inspection and refurbishment, ensuring the best quality. Toyota U Trust customers get certification and warranty of up to 2 Years / 30,000 km, along with three free labor services at any Toyota dealership.
